48,"type":2,"name":"Mater's Tall Tales Season 2","name_cn":"拖线狂想曲第二季","summary":"　　新的一季中，拖线（Larry the Cable Guy 配音）好玩有趣而想象力十足的幻想故事仍在继续。在新的冒险中，他曾经和一架也叫拖线的UFO宝宝玩耍，学会了飞翔的本领；也曾远赴重洋，以进口车的身份在东京参加甩尾王大比拼；还以“拖线喀”的绰号混迹摔角界，挑战一辆辆强壮的大脚卡车；还当过重金属歌手、宇航员、私人侦探，真可谓经历丰富。当然他的好哥们闪电麦昆（Keith Ferguson 配音）还是不相信拖线的信口开河，可是每一次又不由自主地成为拖线故事中的重要角色。真真假假，分辨不清。在私人侦探中，短片还揭示了拖线缺少一盏车头灯的因由。 \r\n 　　拖线狂想曲》为皮克斯继《赛车总动员》后，以配角拖线为主角制作的系列动画短片，供迪斯尼电视频道播放。","date":"2009-11-20","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/94/fe/111248_9tZ79.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/94/fe/111248_9tZ79.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/94/fe/111248_9tZ79.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/94/fe/111248_9tZ79.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/94/fe/111248_9tZ79.jpg"},"rating":{"rank":0,"total":16,"score":6,"count":{"1":0,"2":0,"3":1,"4":2,"5":2,"6":6,"7":3,"8":1,"9":0,"10":1}},"tags":[{"name":"欧美","count":8},{"name":"TV","count":7},{"name":"pixar","count":5},{"name":"2009","count":4},{"name":"短片","count":3},{"name":"美国","count":2},{"name":"原创","count":2},{"name":"3D","count":2},{"name":"皮克斯","count":1},{"name":"Cars","count":1},{"name":"泡面番","count":1}],"eps":6,"collection":{"wish":6,"collect":28,"doing":1,"on_hold":1,"dropped":7}},{"id":127961,"type":2,"name":"Batman: The Brave and the Bold Season 2","name_cn":"蝙蝠侠：英勇无畏 第二季","summary":"","date":"2009-11-20","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/73/8c/127961_huGUg.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/73/8c/127961_huGUg.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/73/8c/127961_huGUg.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/73/8c/127961_huGUg.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/73/8c/127961_huGUg.jpg"},"rating":{"rank":0,"total":8,"score":5.9,"count":{"1":0,"2":0,"3":0,"4":2,"5":0,"6":3,"7":3,"8":0,"9":0,"10":0}},"tags":[{"name":"欧美","count":4},{"name":"TV","count":4},{"name":"dc","count":3},{"name":"蝙蝠侠","count":2},{"name":"美国","count":2},